<li>Ahmadi, R., Ouali, J., Mercier, E., Mansy, J. L., Lanoë, B. V. V., Launeau, P., ... &amp; Rafini, S. (2006). The geomorphologic responses to hinge migration in the fault-related folds in the Southern Tunisian Atlas. Journal of Structural Geology,28(4), 721–728.</li>
